%% Diagram: ABR quality-selection state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Startup
    Startup --> Steady: buffer >= 10s
    Startup --> Startup: keep low quality

    Steady --> RampUp: buffer >= target<br/>and throughput stable
    Steady --> Steady: buffer near target
    Steady --> Defensive: buffer < 50% target

    RampUp --> Steady: quality at top safe rung
    RampUp --> Defensive: throughput drops

    Defensive --> Steady: buffer recovers
    Defensive --> Emergency: buffer < 5s

    Emergency --> Defensive: buffer recovers
    Emergency --> Emergency: drop to lowest rung,<br/>switch OCA if available

    note right of Steady
        safe_bitrate = throughput_estimate * safety_margin
        pick highest rung <= safe_bitrate
    end note
